      "s": "Bloomberg Tech",
      "t": "A Month After SpaceX IPO, Tesla’s Stock Keeps Holding Its Ground",
      "d": "In the weeks leading up to SpaceX’s monster IPO, many Wall Street pros feared the deal represented an existential threat for Elon Musk’s other giant, Tesla Inc. But after a month in the stock market, the outcome is far from clear.",
