      "s": "Bloomberg Tech",
      "t": "Europe's Space Race | Bloomberg Tech: Europe 7/10/2026",
      "d": "In this episode of Bloomberg Tech: Europe, Bloomberg’s Tom Mackenzie launches into Europe's efforts to develop its burgeoning space economy.  SpaceX has shown the might of American space technology - and financial muscle - with its record-breaking IPO. Bloomberg Tech: Europe looks at where Europe is lacking in the space race, and how it can secure space autonomy.\n\n\"Bloomberg Tech: Europe\" spotligh",
